## 🚀 3. PRIORITIZED ACTION PLAN

### 🔴 HIGH IMPACT (Critical Gaps)
- **Add Interactive Visual Statistical Graphs:** Integrate detailed, interactive probability density charts and confidence interval visuals to illustrate test results and distributions, similar to abtestguide.com and speero.com, to enhance user understanding and trust.
- **Implement Real-Time Alerts for Data Quality Issues:** Build warnings for Sample Ratio Mismatch (SRM), low conversion counts, and other data integrity concerns to guide users on test validity and reliability.
- **Incorporate Revenue Impact & ROI Calculations:** Add functionality that links test outcomes to expected monetary impact and business ROI, supporting business-case driven insights.

### 🟡 MEDIUM IMPACT (Opportunity Gaps)
- **Expand Educational Content on Statistical Concepts and A/B Testing Pitfalls:** Develop richer in-tool content—covering hypothesis types, one-sided vs two-sided tests, power analysis, common errors, and best practices integrated into the calculator’s workflow.
- **Enable Multi-Variant Testing Support:** Allow users to input and analyze more than one variant simultaneously to support more complex, real-world experimentation scenarios.
- **Enhance Sample Size Calculator Interactivity:** Make sample size and duration calculators more dynamic with sliders/auto-updating breakdowns to improve usability and comprehension.

### 🟢 LOW IMPACT (Differentiators)
- **Emphasize Bayesian Analysis and Interpretation Guidance:** Strengthen Bayesian probability results presentation with clear explanations to appeal to advanced users and differentiate from frequentist-only calculators.
- **Link Directly to Related Tools and Resources Within the Interface:** Provide easy access to complementary analytics tools, tutorials, and maturity audits to increase engagement and user education.

---

**Summary:** While CXL’s A/B Test Calculator covers the essential features expected by users and competitors, critical enhancements in visual data presentation, actionable alerts, revenue linkage, and depth of educational support are necessary to align with the competitive standard and win the top search rankings. Prioritizing these will not only level up CXL’s offering but also deepen user trust and practical business value.